INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (20004, 'Star Wars Pinball', null, null) ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (153, 'Star Wars Jedi Knight: Jedi Academy', 'Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Jedi Academy, of the highly acclaimed Jedi Knight series, allows players to take on the role of a new student eager to learn the ways of the Force from Jedi Master Luke Skywalker. Interact with famous Star Wars characters in many classic Star Wars locations as you face the ultimate choice: fight for good and freedom on the light side, or follow the path of power and evil to the dark side.', '2003-09-15') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (150, 'Star Wars Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II', 'Whatever path Kyle Katarn chooses will change the face of the galaxy forever.
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (152, 'Star Wars Jedi Knight II: Jedi Outcast', 'In the tradition of the highly acclaimed Star Wars: Jedi Knight series, Star Wars: Jedi Knight 2, Jedi Outcast features rebel agent Kyle Katarn in exhilarating first-person action. Several years have passed since Kyle avenged his father''s death and saved the Valley of the Jedi from Jerec and his band of Dark Jedi. Allowing his Force powers to languish for fear of falling to the dark side, Kyle entrusted his lightsaber to Luke Skywalker, vowing never to use it again. But when a new and menacing threat to the galaxy emerges, Kyle knows he must reclaim his past in order to save his future.
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (206, 'Star Wars Galaxies: Trials of Obi-Wan', 'Star Wars Galaxies: Trials of Obi-Wan was the third expansion pack for the MMO Star Wars Galaxies. 
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (147, 'Star Wars Galaxies: Jump to Lightspeed', 'Star Wars Galaxies: Jump to Lightspeed was the first expansion pack to the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. 
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (146, 'Star Wars Galaxies: Episode III Rage of the Wookiees', 'Star Wars Galaxies: Rage of the Wookiees was the second expansion pack to the MMO Star Wars Galaxies. It was announced on March 9, 2005 and released on May 5, 2005.
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (145, 'Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided', 'Immerse yourself in Star Wars in a way you''ve only dreamed! Find your place during the epic galactic struggle between good and evil, and shape your own destiny. Star Wars Galaxies is the first massively multiplayer online roleplaying game based on the Star Wars universe that lets you live the movies with thousands of other players from around the world!', '2003-06-25') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (140, 'Star Wars Galactic Battlegrounds: Clone Campaigns', 'Expand the battlefield with the Clone Campaigns addon. Choose to play as the breakaway Confederacy of Independent Systems or the Galactic Republic in 14 missions based around characters, vehicles and locations from Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones.', '2002-05-13') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (139, 'Star Wars Galactic Battlegrounds', 'The destiny of a galaxy hangs in the balance, and you are in command. Lead the great armies of the Star Wars: Episode II: Attack of the Clones saga in intense real-time strategy clashes. Enter the fray as the Galactic Empire, Rebel Alliance, Wookies, Trade Federation, Gungans or Royal Naboo to determine the course of the Galactic Civil War.', '2001-11-12') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (6159, 'Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith', 'Third-person action/adventure game, Star Wars: Episode III, delivers the ultimate Jedi action experience as Anakin Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi join forces in fierce battles and heroic lightsaber duels until one''s lust for power and the other''s devotion to duty leads to a final confrontation between good and evil.
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (18951, 'Star Wars Episode II: Attack of the Clones', 'Star Wars Episode II: Attack of the Clones is a side-scrolling action game based on the second movie in the Star Wars prequel trilogy. Players fight through the story of the movie as Obi-Wan Kenobi, Anakin Skywalker, and Mace Windu.', '2002-05-29') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (158, 'Star Wars Episode I: The Phantom Menace', 'Star Wars Episode I: The Phantom Menace is an adventure video game released by LucasArts in 1999. It is based on the film of the same title.', '1999-04-29') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (154, 'Star Wars Episode I: Racer', 'Star Wars: Episode 1: Racer lets you participate in the famous pod race sequence that was the critical highlight of the 1999 film Star Wars: Episode I, The Phantom Menace. These lightning-quick vehicles are capable of reaching simulated speeds of up to 600 miles per hour while skimming a mere 4 feet above the ground. You can race alone or against a friend in split-screen mode on more than 21 courses among eight worlds. Take the controls as Jedi-to-be Anakin Skywalker or any one of over 20 pod racers. Feel the full-force blast while avoiding hazards such as methane lakes, meteor showers, and the unfriendly Tusken Raiders.', '1999-04-30') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (18950, 'Star Wars Episode I: Obi-Wan''s Adventures', null, '2000-11-26') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO games (id, name, summary, release) VALUES (6606, 'Star Wars Episode I: Jedi Power Battles', null, '2000-03-30') ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
